            <h2 class="problem-headline" style="padding:0; margin-bottom:0;">You sit down to work.<br />90 seconds later, you're somewhere else.</h2>

            <p class="problem-opener">You know that moment. Sitting down to start focused work. Then — within 2–5 minutes — you're on a completely different tab, app, or device. You didn't decide to switch. It just happened. Again.</p>

            <p class="problem-intro">And the worst part? It happens before you're even aware of it. Here's how other people describe it in their own words:</p>

