              <h3>The Frint — Your Deep Work Timer</h3>
              <p class="fcard-fdoes">A "Frint" is a timed block of pure creation work. You start one — phone goes away, only real output counts. Coding, writing, strategy. Zero admin. After it ends, you rate how deep your focus actually was. That score gets recorded.</p>
              <p class="fcard-fbenefit">→ So you can see in hard numbers if you actually worked — or just sat near a laptop for 90 minutes.</p>
