              <h3>Your Energy Bar</h3>
              <p class="fcard-fdoes">An algorithm reads your sleep data and converts it into a single battery percentage each morning. Today you're at 78%. Or 29%. Now you know whether to schedule deep creative work — or book calls and easy tasks instead.</p>
              <p class="fcard-fbenefit">→ So you stop forcing 3-hour deep work sessions on 4 hours of sleep and blaming yourself when they fail.</p>
